{"tid":2384362,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人左右身嘅強弱不對稱？","createTime":"2021-01-28T13:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T15:48:46.000Z","uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec82003fe96bf679b81a65eb7ced5fa89c991342","tid":2384362,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:36:40.000Z","msg":"當然太少嘅唔好提啦，大部份人都右邊身強過左邊，但我係講除咗衫照鏡係望得出兩邊身不對稱，強嗰邊大過弱嘅一邊，又或者局部強，例如右腰強過左腰，右背強過左背<br />\n<br />\n我做pull up同push up都似乎幫唔到，好似強嗰一邊永遠都幫緊弱嘅一邊，令弱嘅地方冇機會發展，但我又冇本事做單手引體同push up<br />\n<br />\n冇錢去gym room，有冇啲可以去公園或者家中解決嘅方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dc1aef161356295a316bbbaeb5569a51ed5fb5","tid":2384362,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"做單邊 全部操左邊"},{"pid":"b22dbe60204901a4f386e38e8801addc324c65ee","tid":2384362,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"我唯有選一條低啲嘅bar，掂住地做單手嘅操練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f46fec0b15f2c5a3e7a9546d2f8fe8e730ebcc","tid":2384362,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"左邊強到捉得住青龍，右邊弱到未掌控到隻滑鼠"},{"pid":"21143a243ac4683e382f06b4c9ef0f3ba5e80228","tid":2384362,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"好似強嗰一邊永遠都幫緊弱嘅一邊，令弱嘅地方冇機會發展<br />\n<br />\n你姿勢唔啱"},{"pid":"6b179a8c1ab34606c59f9210995663f084561f60","tid":2384362,"uid":211878,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOrM4fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOrM4fk.png&h=52d052f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df1bd8527191849beefe9e43dea7b8c56293ce59","tid":2384362,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"右邊身由細到大都成日傷<br />\n反而左邊強啲"},{"pid